Class KeyedMessage

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.openxc.messages.VehicleMessage
      • com.openxc.messages.KeyedMessage
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    android.os.Parcelable, java.lang.Comparable<VehicleMessage>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    CanMessage, Command, CommandResponse, CustomCommand, CustomCommandResponse, DiagnosticMessage, MultiFrameResponse, NamedVehicleMessage

    public abstract class KeyedMessage
extends VehicleMessage
    A KeyedMessage is a VehicleMessage with a unique key that identifies this message, and potentially responses to this message. For example, the CAN message ID and bus ID form a unique key for a CAN message.
